[normal]&#xa0;[bold]T[bold]he [bold]R[bold]esidence test  [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“…t
[normal]he test will not apply to the following categories of case (which broadly relate to an individual’s liberty, or where the individual is particularly vulnerable or where the case relates to the protecti
[normal]on of children)...”
[normal]&#xa0;
